title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight and/or map rule.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight and/or map rule.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Create a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table and observe the exception.
